354
00:30:06,730 --> 00:30:08,660
I found out later

355
00:30:10,330 --> 00:30:12,900
Because I seemed genuinely distressed

356
00:30:12,900 --> 00:30:17,600
The police station captain who arrested me conducted a private investigation

357
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:20,460
So I went to find him

358
00:30:22,630 --> 00:30:24,230
Asked him why he helped me

359
00:30:24,230 --> 00:30:26,230
Do you know what he answered?

360
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:28,430
"Your eyes already said it"

361
00:30:30,500 --> 00:30:32,200
"Do you want me to help you?"

362
00:30:35,700 --> 00:30:38,300
He looked incredibly handsome then.

363
00:30:38,300 --> 00:30:39,860
