364
00:30:41,230 --> 00:30:42,630
I want to become a police officer.

365
00:30:43,660 --> 00:30:46,100
To ensure no one is treated unfairly.

366
00:30:46,100 --> 00:30:49,460
I must become an investigator who arrests the real culprits.

